May be this can help,
if it's not "mathematically correct", use data stucture operation,
(TwoDimensionalArray), in other words, you have to coerce yourself
matrix(INT) for example to Matrix(POLY INT))


(205) -> a

          +99  5  5  +
          |          |
   (205)  |9   5  1  |
          |          |
          +1   5  1  +

(206) -> map(i+->i*x,a)

          + 99x  5x  5x  +
          |              |
(206)     | 9x   5x   x  |
          |              |
          +  x  5x   x   +


