> It seems impossible to add 2 anonymous functions. 
> I can compute f(x)+g(x) but I can't use (f+g)(x)
> 
> Can I do (f o g) or can I only compute f(g(x)) = f g x. 
> 
> With mupad (sqrt@@2)(16) and (ln@cos@sin)(PI) compute $2$ and $0$.



